OL,3,CMan told 'we don't serve Protestants'
OL,4,Cin bar wins discrimination case
OL,6,FA Protestant man has settled a case of
OL,7,Freligious discrimination against
OL,8,FBelfast city centre bar owner John
OL,9,FBittle for #6,500.
OL,11,FThe man went to Bittles Bar on a
OL,12,FFriday afternoon to enjoy a drink. As
OL,13,Fhe entered the bar, he met the
OL,14,Flandlord, John Bittles, who he knew
OL,15,Fand had spoken to before.
OL,17,FHowever, he says he was embarrassed
OL,18,Fand felt intimidated by what happened
OL,19,Fnext.
