OL,6,F"The man says that Mr Bittles said to
OL,7,Fhim, 'no seat, no drink, new rules in
OL,8,Fthe bar. I look after my locals'.
OL,10,F"He said that Mr Bittles then pointed
OL,11,Fto a group of men on his left and
OL,12,Fcontinued, 'you have not been in here
OL,13,Ffor about three years and we don't
OL,14,Fserve Protestants, only joking, no I'm
OL,15,Fnot'.'
OL,17,FThe man said the remarks were made
OL,18,F"very loudly and greeted by cheering"
OL,19,Ffrom other customers within the bar.
