OL,6,F"This made him feel very uncomfortable
OL,7,Fand he immediately left the bar. The
OL,8,Fman reported the incident to the PSNI,
OL,9,Fwho recorded it as a hate crime," the
OL,10,Fcommission said.
OL,12,FThe man said he just wanted a drink.
OL,14,F"I'd been to Bittles Bar many times
OL,15,Fbefore over the years. The landlord
OL,16,Fknows me, and I was shocked by his
OL,17,Fcomments and was really concerned by
OL,18,Fthe reaction of the people in the
OL,19,Fbar," he said.
