OL,6,F"I honestly thought the days of this
OL,7,Ftype of behaviour in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fwere behind us. I felt I had to
OL,9,Fchallenge it, so I reported it to the
OL,10,Fpolice and contacted the Equality
OL,11,FCommission."
OL,13,FGeraldine McGahey, Chief Commissioner
OL,14,Fof the Equality Commission for
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland added: "This is a
OL,16,Freminder to all businesses serving the
OL,17,Fpublic that they have responsibilities
OL,18,Funder the anti-discrimination laws.
