OL,6,F"People are protected from religious
OL,7,Fbelief and political opinion
OL,8,Fdiscrimination in the provision of a
OL,9,Fwide range of services. It is
OL,10,Fimportant that customers do not feel
OL,11,Fintimidated or degraded because of
OL,12,Ftheir religious beliefs.
OL,14,F"Everyone who walks through their
OL,15,Fdoors should be treated with dignity
OL,16,Fand respect, no matter what their
OL,17,Freligious background.
