OL,6,F"This is also a reminder for each of
OL,7,Fus that what someone might see as
OL,8,Fbanter or a harmless joke could have
OL,9,Fthe effect of being offensive or
OL,10,Fintimidating to someone else,"
OL,11,Fconcluded Ms McGahey."
OL,13,FThe Equality Commission said, in
OL,14,Fsettling the case, John Bittles
OL,15,Fapologised for any upset and distress
OL,16,Fcaused to the man and affirmed
OL,17,Fcommitment to the principles of
OL,18,Fequality in respect of the provision
OL,19,Fof services to the public. He has also
OL,20,Fagreed to liaise with the Equality
OL,21,FCommission.
